28372,"uid":43026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T20:10:41.000Z","msg":"可以4日唔同醫生 但一定要連續4日咁請"},{"pid":"cb4ab7fa79336b51a259cba9b4a07a94c5b02089","tid":1928372,"uid":24845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"斷開星期六日既就一定唔計連續四日"},{"pid":"dfb7cc3bfb7cf0523b6ffa7ca4c14d9caa3b0cdb","tid":1928372,"uid":288075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"想問如果我本身係返1-5既, 4日出4/5糧係咪要同一張醫生紙? <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">不用同一張,你玩野4日4張不同醫生紙都得</span><br />\n<br />\n如何我星期5睇左一次醫生,有1日SL,之後今日再睇多次醫生,比左3日SL.<br />\n咁樣係咪唔計連續4 日?<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔計呀,斷左星期六日</span><br />\n<br />\n我公司一個月entitled 2日SL,依家咁,我再請星期二三係計no pay?<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">你幾時入職架? eg.做左一年已經儲左24日<br />\n如果你做左一個月,而家有兩日SL balance,扣左上星期五同星期一,星期二三係計no pay</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">自己睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57g_whole.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fcap57g_whole.htm&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=f6dfacbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57g_whole.htm</a></span>"}]}